        "setup": "Create a token in [Vercel account token settings](https://vercel.com/account/tokens). The REST API docs state Vercel Access Tokens are required and sent as `Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>`. You can also mint one from the authenticated API via [Create an Auth Token](https://vercel.com/docs/rest-api/authentication/create-an-auth-token) or manage them with the CLI docs at [vercel tokens](https://vercel.com/docs/cli/tokens)."
